# Testing Required

Every feature/module ships with tests. No merge without them.

| Layer | Tool | Minimum |
|-------|------|---------|
| Go unit | `go test` | Domain logic, validators |
| Go integration | testcontainers | API + RLS leak tests |
| TS unit | Jest/Vitest | hooks, utils, config |
| E2E | Playwright | Critical paths per module |

**Rules:**
- Test behavior, not implementation details.
- Multitenant: always test tenant A cannot read tenant B data.
- Billing: idempotency key replay returns same result.
- Name tests: `TestEstimate_Accept_CreatesJob`.
- Run tests before marking task done.

